des:
Rajneesh also known as Osho, was an Indian mystic and leader of the Rajneesh movement.
Lots of people was and is inspired by him, He's also a spiritual teacher.

Through ages he had a lot of quotes and lessons to say. 
I have database of more than 200 quotes. 
Take one a day and thing deeper about it.
